import React from 'react'; import { Container, Typography, Box, Grid, Card, CardContent, Avatar, Paper } from '@mui/material'; import { School, Restaurant, People, Timeline, Star, TrendingUp } from '@mui/icons-material'; import { UniversityBackground } from '../components/BackgroundStyles'; const EnhancedAboutUs = () => { const stats = [ { icon: , number: '2000+', label: 'Students Served Daily', color: 'primary' }, { icon: , number: '150+', label: 'Sri Lankan Dishes', color: 'secondary' }, { icon: , number: '25', label: 'Dedicated Staff', color: 'success' }, { icon: , number: '10+', label: 'Years of Service', color: 'info' } ]; const achievements = [ { title: 'Best Campus Canteen 2023', description: 'Awarded by University Grants Commission', icon: 'üèÜ' }, { title: 'ISO 22000 Certified', description: 'Food Safety Management System', icon: '‚úÖ' }, { title: '4.8/5 Student Rating', description: 'Based on 5000+ reviews', icon: '‚≠ê' }, { title: 'Zero Waste Initiative', description: 'Eco-friendly operations since 2022', icon: 'üå±' } ]; const teamMembers = [ { name: 'Mr. Sunil Perera', role: 'Canteen Manager', experience: '15 years', image: 'üë®‚Äçüíº' }, { name: 'Mrs. Kamala Silva', role: 'Head Chef', experience: '12 years', image: 'üë©‚Äçüç≥' }, { name: 'Mr. Ravi Fernando', role: 'Operations Supervisor', experience: '8 years', image: 'üë®‚Äçüíª' }, { name: 'Ms. Nisha Jayawardena', role: 'Quality Controller', experience: '6 years', image: 'üë©‚Äçüî¨' } ]; return ( {/* Hero Section with University Image */} üèõÔ∏è University of Ruhuna - Faculty of Technology Canteen Serving authentic Sri Lankan cuisine to our academic community since 2014 Located in the beautiful coastal city of Galle, Southern Province, Sri Lanka {/* Statistics Cards */} {stats.map((stat, index) => ( {stat.icon} {stat.number} {stat.label} ))} {/* University Story Section */} üè´üìöüçõ Our Story The Faculty of Technology Canteen at University of Ruhuna has been the heart of campus dining since 2014. Located in the historic city of Galle, our canteen serves over 2000 students, faculty, and staff daily with authentic Sri Lankan cuisine that reflects our rich cultural heritage. Our mission is to provide nutritious, affordable, and delicious meals while supporting local farmers and suppliers from the Southern Province. We take pride in serving traditional dishes like Rice & Curry, Kottu Rotti, and String Hoppers, prepared with fresh ingredients and authentic spices. As part of the University of Ruhuna family, we understand the importance of good nutrition for academic success and strive to create a welcoming environment for our entire university community. {/* Achievements Section */} Our Achievements & Recognition {achievements.map((achievement, index) => ( {achievement.icon} {achievement.title} {achievement.description} ))} {/* Our Commitment Section */} Our Commitment to Excellence üå± Fresh & Local Sourcing We source our vegetables from local farmers in Galle and Matara districts, ensuring freshness and supporting our community. Our rice comes directly from paddy fields in the Southern Province. üí∞ Student-Friendly Prices Our meals are subsidized by the university to ensure every student can enjoy nutritious food without financial burden. A complete meal costs less than Rs. 200. üá±üá∞ Authentic Sri Lankan Flavors Every dish is prepared using traditional Sri Lankan recipes passed down through generations. Our chefs are trained in authentic Southern Province cooking methods. üìö Student Convenience Beyond food, we provide essential stationery and study materials. Our digital ordering system helps students save time and focus on their studies. {/* Team Section */} Meet Our Dedicated Team The passionate people behind your daily meals {teamMembers.map((member, index) => ( {member.image} {member.name} {member.role} {member.experience} experience ))} {/* Location & Hours */} Visit Us üìç Location Faculty of Technology
University of Ruhuna
Hapugala, Galle 80000
Southern Province, Sri Lanka Just 5 minutes walk from the main lecture halls and library üïí Operating Hours Monday - Friday:
‚Ä¢ Breakfast: 7:00 AM - 9:00 AM
‚Ä¢ Lunch: 12:00 PM - 2:00 PM
‚Ä¢ Dinner: 6:00 PM - 8:00 PM
‚Ä¢ Stationery Shop: 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM Saturday: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM
Sunday: Closed ); }; export default EnhancedAboutUs;
